        {
            "title": "日本將新發行11.7萬億日圓債券 為經濟刺激方案提供資金",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"637\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/b_YOb8Jb63Ak3ijf4x.BWw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzNztjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/f6db962dec91b9e85451985af1f6f005\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 日本首相高市早苗的政府計畫新發更多債券為經濟刺激方案提供資金，正值市場對該國公共財政狀況及殖利率上升的擔憂持續發酵之際。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博周四看到的一份文件顯示，總額約18.3萬億日圓（1170億美元）的追加預算將通過增發11.7萬億日圓債券來籌措資金。政府還計畫動用2.9萬億日圓的稅收盈餘、約1萬億日圓的非稅收入以及上財年約2.7萬億日圓的未動用資金來控制舉債。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管如此，新增債務規模仍高於前首相石破茂一年前出台經濟措施時6.7萬億日圓的債券增發額。預計日本內閣將於周五批准這份追加預算案。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b62fced7-83f8-308f-8db0-abc3f8527768-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"637\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DY6Zh3CXkr_9b524_vQ.4A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzNztjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/f9704a04b2db4e5f62088925762af6f2\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這份追加預算凸顯出高市在平衡其刺激經濟立場與維持負責任財政目標方面所面臨的挑戰。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資者對高市領導下日本長期財政狀況的擔憂持續發酵。本月早些時候，日本長期國債殖利率攀升至二十多年來的最高水平，日圓匯率則維持相對疲軟態勢。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">為了安撫市場，高市上周暗示本財年的債券發行總額將低於上財年。2024財年日本發行了42.1萬億日圓的債券，用於為常規預算和追加預算提供資金。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">加上最新的這11.7萬億日圓，本財年的債券發行總額將達到40.3萬億日圓，比上財年少約4.3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Japan to Issue $75 Billion in New Bonds to Fund Economic Package</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Yuko Takeo.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E6%93%AC%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%8C%E9%80%BE11-5%E8%90%AC%E5%84%84%E6%97%A5%E5%9C%93%E6%96%B0%E5%82%B5%E7%82%BA%E5%88%BA%E6%BF%80%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB%E7%B1%8C%E8%B3%87-143331907.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-27 16:05:48",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "台灣利率市場：10年券利率升至逾一周高位 券商觀望國防預算；短率平",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 聯儲會最新褐皮書報告顯示就業疲軟，或為聯儲會12月降息創造條件，交易員繼續為降息押注建倉，10年美債殖利率隔夜走低；在殖利率連跌兩日後，台債10年殖利率周四微幅收升，回到逾一周高位。</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">統一證券在報告中稱，美國勞動數據不佳使美債利率先上後下，但對台債影響有限</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">元大證券報告稱，總統賴清德宣布未來國防特別預算，預計投入1.25兆元提升國防自主及壯大國防產業，受明年起台灣公債籌碼供應恐增加的影響，台債整體買盤追價動力或轉趨保守</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">貨幣市場</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b8810952-0972-35af-92bb-4110b58f230c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據票券商與銀行人士稱，周四銀行資金不均的情形顯著，使市場氛圍偏緊，部分銀行因自身資金狀況而減少與票券商新承作拆款，不過尚未對票券商整體的資金調度造成明顯影響；短票與拆款利率持平。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據兩位銀行資金調度人士稱，同業資金多缺不一；其中一位稱拆款交易偏平淡，另一位則稱有一些新增的銀行有資金需求</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據兩位票券商人士表示，一些銀行無法新增拆款，但與銀行到期續做短票與拆款足以使自身資金調度無虞</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與銀行承作30天期的自保短票利率主要在1.45%-1.46%，以1.46%居多</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與銀行承做跨月拆款利率在1.44%，同上日</p></li></ul></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上述交易員不願具名接受採訪，因未被授權公開評論</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台灣短票市場：30天自保票上日平均利率1.454%</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場動態</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據彭博追蹤櫃買中心數據，10年熱券成交在1.305%，升0.62基點；成交1.0億元台幣</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">5年熱券電子盤無成交</p></li></ul></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台股加權指數上漲0.53%，報27554.53點</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據彭博數據，5年期利率交換報1.8%，升2.0基點</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國10年期國債殖利率紐約尾盤報3.9941%，亞洲盤中報3.9941%</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台北時間14:01，據拆款中心數據，隔夜拆款加權平均利率在0.819%，區間在0.805%-0.82%，上日收在0.825%</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2-7天平均利率在1.383%，區間在1.2%-1.46%</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上交易日當日超額準備為1300.0億元台幣；本提存期累計超額準備為1兆287億元台幣，加計前期1%超額準備為1兆2174億元台幣</p></li></ul></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至上交易日，央行定存單未到期餘額為7兆2710億元台幣，上日增發65.0億元</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">參看台灣央行各天期存單到期落點一覽，點選WSL TWNCD</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">重點關注</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國上周首次申領失業救濟人數降至21.6萬 為4月中旬以來最低</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩根大通預計聯儲會12月將降息 改變之前按兵不動的預測</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯儲會褐皮書顯示經濟活動變化不大 整體消費者支出進一步下降</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">韓國央行政策聲明移除降息立場相關措辭 但稱對降息可能保持開放(1)</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4-10%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%B8%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E5%8D%87%E8%87%B3%E9%80%BE-%E5%91%A8%E9%AB%98%E4%BD%8D-%E5%88%B8%E5%95%86%E8%A7%80%E6%9C%9B%E5%9C%8B%E9%98%B2%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97-%E7%9F%AD%E7%8E%87%E5%B9%B3-062856154.html",
